title: $250 Moving Incentive***2 Bedroom Uptown Apartment-2514 Emerson

posting_body: ['Beautiful 2 BR apartment available in the heart of Uptown.', 'Walk to Byerly’s, run around Lake of Isles, and hop on to the bus.', 'Couple of minutes drive to DT Mpls, UofM, and South Mpls.', 'Enjoy the best of Mpls living in one of the most vibrant neighborhoods with so many eateries a walking distance away.', 'Beautiful vintage building with all modern amenities.', 'The unit features: - 2 Bedroom/1 Bathroom - Hard Wood floors - built ins with updated kitchen with granite countertop (some units have dishwashers)', 'The building features - Onsite laundry, dedicated storage units, and Off-Street parking.', 'Utilities include Heat, Water & Sewer paid by management.', 'Tenant responsible for Electricity.', '12 month lease.', 'Shorter leases maybe available.', '*****$250 moving incentive if Leased by September 1, 2022 !!!!!!!', "Don't miss out on this great apartment!", 'Please contact us for showing.', 'Keywords: Uptown, DT, DT Minneapolis, University of Minnesota, UofM, South Minneapolis, Lake Calhoun, Bde Maka Ska, Lake of Isles, Lake Harriet, Hennepin, Lyndale, Franklin, Wedge']
